ScrollWithin jQuery plugin

This jQuery plugin allows to scroll within page using a simple menu linked to section ids and performing a smooth scrolling animation.

EXAMPLE:

$('.nav').scrollWithin({options});

OPTIONS:

active_class: 'active',                 -> (class to apply to menu item when active)
margin: 0,                              -> (margin in pixel scroll.top)
parent: false,                          -> (apply active class to parent item)
duration: 'slow',                       -> (duration of transition scroll)
easing: null,                           -> (easing type. req. easing plugin)
hash: false,                            -> (add hash to URL)
onClickMenu: function() {},             -> (callback onClick)
onScrollComplete: function() {},        -> (callback onScroll)


LIVE DEMO:

http://ondelab.com